movie.title: Beyond the Sea
movie.plot: Based on the life and career of legendary entertainer, Bobby Darin, the biopic moves back and forth between his childhood and adulthood, to tell the tale of his life.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 6 nominations.

events.title: John Gotti becomes the new head of the Gambino family

movie.title: Gotti
movie.plot: John Gotti rises to the top of the New York underworld to become the boss of the Gambino crime family. His life takes a tumultuous turn as he faces tragedy, multiple trials and a prison sentence.

events.title: the date of Bucky's Mission Report

movie.title: Captain America: Civil War
movie.plot: Following the events of Age of Ultron, the collective governments of the world pass an act designed to regulate all superhuman activity. This polarizes opinion amongst the Avengers, causing two factions to side with Iron Man or Captain America, which causes an epic battle between former allies.
